{"title":"内蒙古——为自治区成立五十周年而作（外三首）","authors":["乌力吉"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":7,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"内蒙古"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为自治区成立五十周年而作（外三首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内蒙古自治区人民政府主席乌力吉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山兴安贺兰耸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绵延云雨朔天苍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼伦锡林草原美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿中缀红莽无疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"额水辽洪黄河亘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史变迁水汤汤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八千里路山川秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二千多万儿女情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东林西铁遍地宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南粮北牧稀土王。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青城鹿郭天骄地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁塔电索亮四方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳不落金榜曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科研明星试管羊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首颗卫星裂长空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半个世纪多昂扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大兴安岭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩瀚的绿海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鹰的翅膀拍不尽它的细浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参天的落叶松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融入苍穹的襟怀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罩在林顶的白云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是随风飘向远方的手帕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂的朝霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别有天神的风姿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掠过一阵大风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林海涌起万顷碧波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾盆大雨的洗礼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个像是出水芙蓉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝枝叶叶舞动乐声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着松涛的风韵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清泉叮咚，鸟语花香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山河回响，獐奔鹿鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林这广袤的世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宛如另一个海底。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩靠肩的密林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只留出立足的寸土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要想飞出原始森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天只有一丝神秘的微笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大自然的鬼斧神工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裁出你美丽的裙裾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养育生命的摇篮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造出数不清的人间奇迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史珍藏得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方显出这动人的风姿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳总是那么红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又那么圆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万紫千红的鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐出缕缕清凉的香风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坦荡博大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是父亲的胸怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温柔蕴藉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像母爱醇厚绵长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛羊走过的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便有乳汁般的小河在低吟浅唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天和绿海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是所有生命的源。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土默川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敕勒古歌吟荒凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今良田着绿装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朔漠轶事存孤壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云中春风拂柳杨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河穿腾土默川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山雄姿耸脊梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞外风光今日好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代变迁几沧桑。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}